Technologies used

node.js				http://www.nodejs.org
Node Packet Manager		http://npmjs.org/
Express Web Framework		http://expressjs.com/
Jade				http://github.com/visionmedia/jade
Dojo JS Toolkit			http://dojotoolkit.org
Mongoose			http://www.learnboost.com/mongoose/
MongoDB				http://www.mongodb.org
Connect				http://www.senchalabs.org/connect/


Before starting the app

1. Install node
2. Install NPM
3. Use NPM to install express and jade (npm install express && npm install jade && npm install mongoose && npm install mongodb && npm install connect)
4. Download Mongoose, unpack it
5. Run the app


puedes instalar forever o nodemon, yo uso nodemon.




